    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      int DestinationID
      Called when the plugin is instantiated (before {@link #resume}) to supply the destination ID. Since a given plugin class may be used by multiple destinations, this allows each instance to know what destination it is associated with. Implementors of this interface will typically store the destinationID in a member variable of the implementing class for later use in logging, etc.
